text: Franklin Six (born 29 December 1996 in Ploegsteert) is a Belgian cyclist, who currently rides for UCI ProTeam . ==Major results== ;2016 : 8th Rund um den Finanzplatz Eschborn-Frankfurt U23 ;2017 : 2nd Road race, National Under–23 Road Championships : 5th Liège–Bastogne–Liège U23 ;2019 : 10th Paris–Chauny ==References== ==External links== * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian male cyclists
title: Franklin Six
